line_1: Fond of applause, he sought the feasts
And, in the Structure of their Feasts,
line_2: They seek to feed, and please their Guests:

line_1: No Lobster on the little Captive feasts;
line_2: Nor crawling Preke those harmless Shores molests.

line_1: Their wedding garments prove their wedding feasts,
line_2: And the bride's fin'ry entertains the guests:
